n Age: Origins]]''|| BioWare || {{Ya}} || {{Na}} || <ref name=\"GameZone\"/>\n|-\n| ''[[Dragon Age II]]'' || BioWare || {{Ya}} || {{Na}} || <ref name=\"eaaccess\">https://www.ea.com/ea-access/games#xbox-one-only</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Dragon Age: Inquisition]]'' || BioWare || {{Ya}} || {{Ya}} || <ref name=\"Titanfall and DAI\"/>\n|-\n| ''[[Fe (video game)|Fe]]'' || [[Zoink]] || {{Ya}} || {{Ya}} || <ref>{{cite tweet|user=EAAccess|author=EA Access|number=1030137148098281474|title=Speak the language of the forest and defeat the Silent Ones in Fe. Now in the EA Access library!|date=August 16, 2018|accessdate=August 16, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Feeding Frenzy (video game)|Feeding Frenzy]]'' || PopCap Games || {{Ya}} || {{Na}} || <ref name=\"EAA-Late16\"/>\n|-\n| ''[[Feeding Frenzy 2]]'' || PopCap Games || {{Ya}} || {{Na}} || <ref name=\"EAA-Late16\"/>\n|-\n| ''[[FIFA 14]]'' || [[EA Canada]] || {{Ya}} || {{Na}} || Launch title for the app.<ref name=\"GS-Vault\"/> Delisted on October 18, 2017.<ref>https://www.ea.com/ea-access/news/fifa-14-will-leave-ea-access-on-october-18</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[FIFA 15]]'' || EA Canada || {{Ya}} || {{Na}} || <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.destructoid.com/fifa-15-now-included-in-ea-access-291805.phtml|title=FIFA 15 now included in EA Access|first=Jordan|last=Devore|work=[[Destructoid]]|date=May 8, 2015|accessdate=May 9, 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[FIFA 16]]'' || EA Canada || {{Ya}} || {{Na}} || <ref name=\"Fifa 16\">{{cite web|url=https://www.easports.com/fifa/news/2016/fifa-16-in-the-vault?cid=4226&ts=1459872828772 |title=FIFA 16 Coming Soon to The Vault |website=Easports.com |date= |accessdate=2016-04-11}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[FIFA 17]]'' || [[EA Vancouver]] || {{Ya}} || {{Ya}} || <ref>{{cite web |last=Dayus |first=Oscar |date=April 21, 2017 |url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/new-eaorigin-access-game-out-now-for-xbox-one-and-/1100-6449520/ |title=New EA/Origin Access Game Out Now For Xbox One And PC |publisher=[[GameSpot]] |accessdate=April 21, 2017}}</r