N]]<br /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/alec-benjamin/chart-history/canadian-hot-100|title=Alec Benjamin Chart History: Canadian Hot 100|work=Billboard|accessdate=January 23, 2019}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"| [[Hitlisten|DEN]]<br /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://hitlisten.nu/default.asp?w=10&y=2019&list=t40|title=Track Top-40 Uge 10, 2019|publisher=Hitlisten|accessdate=March 20, 2019}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"| [[Irish Singles Chart|IRE]]<br /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://irma.ie/index.cfm?page=irish-charts&chart=Singles|title=IRMA \u2013 Irish Charts|publisher=[[Irish Recorded Music Association]]|accessdate=April 13, 2019}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"| [[Single Top 100|NLD]]<br /><ref name=\"NLD\"/>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"| [[VG-lista|NOR]]<br /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vglista.no/topplister/topp-20-single-2019-07/|title=VG-lista \u2013 Topp 20 Single uke 7, 2019|publisher=[[VG-lista]]|accessdate=February 16, 2019}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"| [[Sverigetopplistan|SWE]]<br /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sverigetopplistan.se/chart/41?dspy=2019&dspp=15|title=Veckolista Singlar, vecka 15|publisher=[[Sverigetopplistan]]|accessdate=April 12, 2019}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"| [[Swiss Hitparade|SWI]]<br /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://hitparade.ch/song/Alec-Benjamin/Let-Me-Down-Slowly-1766165|title=Alec Benjamin \u2013 Let Me Down Slowly|website=hitparade.ch|accessdate=January 21, 2019}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"| [[UK Singles Chart|UK]]<br /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.officialcharts.com/artist/55025/alec-benjamin/|title=Alec Benjamin {{!}} full Official Chart history|publisher=[[Official Charts Company]]|accessdate=February 2, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Paper Crown\"\n| 2014<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.warnermusic.com.